<br>
As for people, no one talked to anyone. No one answered questions, no one helped anyone. If you think finding a group in EQ is tough, try AO. when I played ( for 3 months) almost no one was willing to work together. I think I had 3 groups the whole time.<br>
<br>
Weapons have to be upgraded as you level, a level 6 gun isnt much good in a level 12 encounter. Some weapons are found in missions some are found by adventurering. Some have to be bought. Same with augments and armor.<br>
<br>
